content.text:
Praise Yah!
Oh give thanks to Yahweh, for He is good;
For His lovingkindness endures forever.

Our fathers in Egypt did not consider Your wondrous deeds;
They did not remember Your abundant lovingkindnesses,
But they rebelled by the sea, at the Red Sea.

Many times He would deliver them;
But they were rebellious in their counsel,
And so they sank down in their iniquity.
